I found one production edge the handoff did not cover: adding `index.ts` makes this manifest discoverable as a bundled plugin, so an explicit plugin enable would import the stub. A bare exported constant bundles, but it is not a valid OpenClaw plugin module; I’m changing the stub to a no-op `definePluginEntry` so discovery, bundling, and explicit enablement all remain non-destructive.
